Don Starr https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_Starr 0 Donald "Don" Starr (September 20, 1917 – July 11, 1995) was an American actor who became known for his recurring role as oil baron Jordan Lee in the CBS-TV primetime soap opera series Dallas.
